          <td valign="Top" align="left"><img src="/pykyra-stuff/pykyra.gif" alt=" "></td>
          <td><h2>a fast game development framework for Python</h2></td>
        </tr>
  </tbody>    
</table>

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Base classes: Sprite, Canvas, Image, Tile, ...</li>
	<li>MPEG video support</li>
	<li>Render in an OpenGL surface support</li>
	<li>Compressed data files for package images, sprites, etc..</li>
	<li>PNG, JPEG, GIF, BMP, TIF, PCX, etc. images support (directly or from a .dat file)</li>
	<li>MP3, Ogg Vorbis, WAV and multichannel module files support</li>
	<li>Sound channels mixing</li>
	<li>many others: alpha channel, scaling, etc.</li>
</ul>
<br>

<h3>Latest version</h3>

<p>Source Code</p>
